        "label": "Permanent Effects",
        "value": "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">Gain&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><abbr title=\"Destiny\"><span class=\"ipsEmoji\"><abbr title=\"Destiny\">ü§û</abbr></span></abbr></strong><strong>&nbsp;<em><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">(one&nbsp;<abbr title=\"Resource which can be spent to reroll any dice, and activate powerful effects\"><abbr title=\"Resource which can be spent to reroll any dice, and activate powerful effects\">Destiny</abbr></abbr>)&nbsp;</span></em><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">at the beginning of each Scene&nbsp;<em>(to a total of&nbsp;</em></span></strong><strong><em><abbr title=\"Destiny\"><span class=\"ipsEmoji\"><abbr title=\"Destiny\">ü§û</abbr></span></abbr></em></strong><strong><em>&nbsp;</em></strong><strong><em><abbr title=\"Destiny\"><span class=\"ipsEmoji\"><abbr title=\"Destiny\">ü§û</abbr></span></abbr></em></strong><strong><em>&nbsp;</em></strong><strong><em><abbr title=\"Destiny\"><span class=\"ipsEmoji\"><abbr title=\"Destiny\">ü§û</abbr></span></abbr></em></strong><strong><em><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">&nbsp;with the previous levels of Luck Bending)</span></em></strong><strong><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">.</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">You become aware when a&nbsp;<abbr title=\"Any Character: NPC or Protagonist\"><abbr title=\"Any Character: NPC or Protagonist\">Character</abbr></abbr>&nbsp;attempts any d100 roll within&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><abbr title=\"Range\"><span class=\"ipsEmoji\"><abbr title=\"Range\">üìè</abbr></span></abbr></strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\"><abbr title=\"How far can an effect be applied\"><abbr title=\"How far can an effect be applied\">Range</abbr></abbr>:&nbsp;<abbr title=\"Requires minimum 7 Hexagons to cross\"><abbr title=\"Requires minimum 7 Hexagons to cross\">Building [Area 3]</abbr></abbr>.</span></strong></p>"
