      "AdditionalInfo": {
        "type": "text",
        "dtype": "String",
        "label": "Effect Additional Information",
        "value": "<p align=\"center\"><em><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">&nbsp;</span></em><em><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">Example</span></em></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><em><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">I am attempting to make a&nbsp;<abbr title=\"Takes your One Action slot and allows multiple One Actions for a -10% reduction for each Action to all Actions\"><abbr title=\"Takes your One Action slot and allows multiple One Actions for a -10% reduction for each Action to all Actions\">Multi-Action</abbr></abbr>&nbsp;which involves two Main Actions, each to be attempted with a &ndash; 20% reduction due to the&nbsp;<abbr title=\"Takes your One Action slot and allows multiple One Actions for a -10% reduction for each Action to all Actions\"><abbr title=\"Takes your One Action slot and allows multiple One Actions for a -10% reduction for each Action to all Actions\">Multi-Action</abbr></abbr>. Furthermore, the&nbsp;<abbr title=\"The one who Narrates the Saga\"><abbr title=\"The one who Narrates the Saga\">Narrator</abbr></abbr>&nbsp;imposed a &ndash; 30%&nbsp;<abbr title=\"A decrease at a specific roll\"><abbr title=\"A decrease at a specific roll\">Penalty</abbr></abbr>&nbsp;to the first attempted roll. My&nbsp;<abbr title=\"A Player's Character\"><abbr title=\"A Player's Character\">Protagonist</abbr></abbr>&nbsp;has already successfully activated Thaumaturgy and accumulated&nbsp;</span></em><em><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\"><abbr title=\"Level of Success\"><span class=\"ipsEmoji\"><abbr title=\"Level of Success\">‚úîÔ∏è</abbr></span></abbr></span></em><em><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">. As I result, I choose to ignore the&ndash; 30%&nbsp;<abbr title=\"A decrease at a specific roll\"><abbr title=\"A decrease at a specific roll\">Penalty</abbr></abbr>&nbsp;from my initial roll. I can spend my&nbsp;</span></em><em><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\"><abbr title=\"Level of Success\"><span class=\"ipsEmoji\"><abbr title=\"Level of Success\">‚úîÔ∏è</abbr></span></abbr>&nbsp;</span></em><em><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">to further ignore any one of the two &ndash; 20% reductions from any of the rolls.</span></em></p>"
