    "Description": {
      "type": "text",
      "dtype": "String",
      "label": "Metapower Description",
      "value": "<p align=\"center\"><em><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">By unlocking this advanced level of the Metapower: Luck Bending, your cosmic luck begins to fully unfold. You can mitigate the ramifications of your labors, or that of others, from a safe distance. Furthermore, with Thaumaturgy, you can reactively send a surge of bad luck to any adversary that is clearly detectable to you and give them a tough break. As your power of Luck Bending expands, you feel an invisible thread connecting you to the ebb and flow of destiny itself. With a mere thought, you can nudge the cosmic scales and tilt them in your favor.</span></em></p>"
